    What is a team photo?
    A team composite photo is a single image that combines individual portraits of team members into a unified group display. These photos are often used when it's not possible to gather the entire team in one location for a traditional group photo.23-Jan-2025

    How to make a team photo?
    Place the Teams in Rows

    Depending on the size of the team, you can determine how many rows are needed and how many players should be in each row. By adjusting the length of the rows and alternating the number of players in each row, you can create a harmonious photo that fits within the traditional aspect ratio.

    How to create a Teams picture?
    To change your team image:
    1. Go to the team you'd like to update the picture for.
    2. Hover over the the team name to select More options > Manage team . ...
    3. In the Settings tab, expand Team details and select Change picture. ...
    4. Select Upload to choose a new image from your files, or Remove. ...
    5. Select Save to save your new team picture.
